longBusinessSummary: TMM, Inc., a technology company, offers digital video compression and playback software in the United States. It offers TMMI Mini PC X, a small form factor fully functional Windows 10-64 computer; TRUDEF video player, a universal windows platform (UWP) compliant with a custom internal video pipeline designed to improve HEVC and AV1 visual quality on large resolution screens; and TRUDEF VDK3 fractal video codec. The company was formerly known as Total Multimedia Inc. and changed its name to TMM, Inc. in 2001. TMM, Inc. was founded in 1990 and is based in Surfside Beach, South Carolina.
